    {
      "id": "overview",
      "title": "Role Overview",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "Solutions Architect interviews assess your ability to design technical solutions for customers while communicating effectively with both technical and business stakeholders."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "**What interviewers assess:**\n\n- Technical breadth across cloud/infrastructure\n- Architecture design skills\n- Customer communication and requirements gathering\n- Ability to translate business needs to technical solutions\n- Pre-sales and technical advisory experience"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "format",
      "title": "Common Interview Format",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "content": {
            "text": "**Typical SA interview loop:**\n\n1. **Recruiter screen** (30 min)\n2. **Hiring manager screen** (60 min)\n3. **Onsite/Virtual loop** (4-5 hours):\n   - Technical deep dive/architecture design\n   - Customer scenario role play\n   - Whiteboard architecture session\n   - Behavioral/leadership round"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "tip",
          "content": {
            "text": "Practice presenting technical architectures to non-technical audiences. The ability to simplify without losing accuracy is crucial."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
